<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Murr! by Lev Y</title>
    <link
        href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link
        href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.2.0/fonts/remixicon.css"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/themes/base/jquery-ui.css"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link
        href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/noUiSlider/14.6.3/nouislider.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
    <style>
        .filter-sidebar {
            position: -webkit-sticky;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            max-height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .search-bar {
            position: -webkit-sticky;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1020;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .search-bar .input-group {
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .search-bar .form-control {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .card-horizontal {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        .card-horizontal img {
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .card-horizontal .card-body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .sticky-footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 20vh;
            right: 20vh;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 10px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            z-index: 1050;
        }

        .contact-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .contact-form, .contact-image {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        .contact-image {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .contact-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .filter-sidebar {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }

            .filter-sidebar.show {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }

            .card-horizontal {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: row;
            }

            .card-horizontal img {
                width: 150px;
                height: auto;
            }

            .card-horizontal .card-body {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .sticky-footer {
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
            }

            .contact-image {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- navbar-->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg justify-content-between sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="">
                <h3 class="logo mt-1">😺 Murr<span>!</span></h3>
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                data-bs-target="navbarSupportedContent"
                aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false"
                aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <h2 class="mt-2"><i class="ri-menu-fold-2-line"></i></h2>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="about">מידע חיוני</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link store-link" href="store">החנות
                            הורטואלית</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="contact">צור קשר</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-section" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="nav-item col-4">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="liked">
                            <h5 class="mt-2"><i
                                    class="ri-heart-fill active"></i></h5>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nav-item col-4">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="cart">
                            <h5 class="mt-2"><i class="ri-shopping-cart-fill">
                            </h5></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nav-item col-4">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="profile">
                            <h5 class="mt-2"><i class="ri-user-fill"></i></h5>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <a href="" class="btn btn-brand ms-lg-3">Download</a> -->
        </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- navbar-->
    <!-- cart -->
    <section id="cart" class="min-vh-100 d-flex">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="my-4">צור קשר</h1>
            <div class="contact-container">
                <div class="contact-image">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300" alt="חתול">
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">אנחנו כאן כדי לעזור!</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">אם יש לכם שאלות, הצעות או בעיות, אל תהססו לפנות אלינו באמצעות הטופס הבא:</p>
                            <form>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="name">שם</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="הכנס את שמך">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="email">דוא"ל</label>
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="הכנס את כתובת הדוא"ל שלך">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="message">הודעה</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="5" placeholder="כתוב את הודעתך כאן"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">שלח</button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">פרטי יצירת קשר</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                <strong>כתובת:</strong> רחוב הקניות 123, תל אביב, ישראל<br>
                                <strong>טלפון:</strong> 03-1234567<br>
                                <strong>דוא"ל:</strong> support@store.com
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- </section> -->
    <!-- cart -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>